Class SystemConfig

java.lang.Object
spss.project.backend.configuration.system.SystemConfig
public class SystemConfig extends Object
This class represents a configuration for the system. The configuration is stored in the database and contains information about the system such as the default paper supply date, the file types that are allowed and the user who created the configuration.
